  <summary date="2020-06-23T19:53:52Z" status="Introduced in House">No Bailouts for Illegal Aliens Act

This bill withholds funding authorized under the Coronavirus Aid, Relief, and Economic Security Act (CARES Act) from any state or municipality that provides relief payments through a program targeted exclusively to individuals who are believed to be unlawfully present in the United States.</summary>
